name: Git with Karagdon!
body:
Katherine Reyes.  Web developer from Seattle, Washington. She currently holds Bachelors of Arts in Marketing and Information Systems from Seattle University, which is also in Seattle, Washington. (2013)

Also, she loves cats, comic books, ice cream, and skateboarding on sunny days. 

### Projects:
* [2013 - TeemOP1] (http://karagdon.github.com/teemop1/index.html) - Logo Design, HTML5 + CSS3 Formatting and User-triggered(hover) events though Flexbox, experiments in webkits.

* [2013 - BOCK: The Board Game Clock] (http://karagdon.github.com/bock/index.html) - Uses JavaScript to handle user and timed events.

* [2013 - Beacon Food Forest](http://karagdon.github.com/bffsite/index.html) - Turned [Jill DelSordi](http://www.whitewindowstudios.com)'s design into a fully functional website!

### Technical Skills:
* Design: Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator
* Web: HTML5, CSS3, JQuery, JavaScript, PHP, C#, VisualBasic, .Net, XML
